  "calendarNotes": "Prince William County Public Schools begins the 2026–2027 school year on August 24, 2026. Spring Break runs March 22–26, aligning with Fairfax County Public Schools and Loudoun County Public Schools. Unlike many nearby districts, PWCS also closes for Eid al-Fitr on March 10 before Spring Break later that month. The school year ends June 17, 2027."
